    Title: Harijan
    Editor: Mohandas Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 20 April 1934
---
The 'touch-me-not'ism that disfigures the present-day Hinduism is a morbid
growth. It only betrays a woodenness of mind, a blind self-conceit. It is
abhorrent alike to the spirit of religion and morality.
